  "content": "          <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">No file size limit on log reads. One large file could OOM the server.</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"insight-box\">\n    <p>These aren't edge cases. They're the kind of bugs that pass every test and break in production. The kind a teammate would catch in a PR review.</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"flex-grow\"></div>\n  <div class=\"author-tag\">Lim Chun Zhe</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-number\">02 / 09</div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SLIDE 3: THE EVOLUTION -->\n<div class=\"slide\">\n  <div class=\"slide-label\">The Iteration</div>\n  <div class=\"slide-title\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\">\n    From \"Review This\"<br>\n    <span class=\"highlight-cyan\">to Five Personas</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"slide-subtitle\" style=\"font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    Each iteration caught things the previous one couldn't.\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- Evolution steps -->\n  <div class=\"evo-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--text-muted);\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\">\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">V1: \"Review this diff\"</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">Generic feedback. Everything is \"looks good\" with surface-level suggestions.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--text-muted); letter-spacing: 1px;\">GENERIC</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"evo-arrow\">&#8595;</div>\n\n  <div class=\"evo-step\" style=\"border-left: 4px solid var(--accent-amber);\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;\">\n      <div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700;\">V2: One reviewer with a role</div>\n        <div style=\"font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-secondary); margin-top: 4px;\">\"You are a senior SWE.\" Immediately better. Started flagging real bugs.</div>\n      </div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent-amber); letter-spacing: 1px;\">FOCUSED</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"evo-arrow\">&#8595;</div>",
